# Google OAuth 2.0 Client ID
# How to get one: https://developers.google.com/identity/gsi/web/guides/get-google-api-clientid
# Note: Google Sign-in requires origins to be 'localhost' or a secure domain (HTTPS).
# Raw IP addresses like 192.168.2.5 are NOT supported as Authorized JavaScript Origins by Google.
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your-google-client-id-here.apps.googleusercontent.com
